          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Light' fontsize='10'>N: North placed 21/51 Electronics orders (41.2%) but contributed ₹20.27M, only 33.2% of total Electronics revenue (₹61.02M). R: North’s average Electronics order (₹965K) is far below the global average (₹1,196K) — smaller order sizes. A: Audit North’s sales discounting pattern and introduce volume‑based pricing (e.g. 10% off on 5+ units) to lift average order value to the global average.</run>
