            <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Light' fontsize='10'>N: Electronics products generate ₹61.02M (91.5% of total ₹66.70M). R: High‑value items (Laptops, Smartphones, Speakers) dominate sales; Software &amp; Accessories are vastly under‑represented. A: Launch a “Smart Office Bundle” (Laptop + Cloud Storage + Keyboard) to force cross‑category purchasing and reduce concentration risk from 91% → 75% within 2 quarters.</run>
