            <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Light' fontsize='10'>N: Top 5 products — Laptop (₹18.07M), Smartwatch (₹12.31M), Speaker (₹12.04M), Smartphone (₹7.61M), Headphones (₹5.65M) — sum ₹55.67M, 83.5% of total ₹66.70M. R: These high‑value Electronics SKUs are essential for corporate clients, but their dominance creates supply‑chain risk. A: Negotiate quarterly vendor‑managed inventory for exactly these 5 SKUs to guarantee 98% stock availability, while allocating 10% marketing budget to the next 5 products to build a broader base.</run>
